description	"Jedi Watchman

^2Weaponry:
- Lightsaber Staff
-- Staff / Yellow Styles
-- Saber Defense (3)
-- Blaster Defense   (2)
-- Blaster Deflect (2)

^5Force Powers:
- Jump  (2)
- Push  (2)
- Sense (3)
- Speed (2)
- Mind Trick (3)

^8Attributes:
- Shroud [Force Sense Immunity]
- Force Block (2)
- Force Focus (1)
- Reinforcements (1)

Studying special Force techniques to better equip themselves for their missions, Watchmen were skilled at fading into the background, allowing them to subtly manipulate political events in a benevolent fashion to sustain peace and prosperity."